title: WAITING _FOR_ GOD_ SERIES4_ D1
description:
Yet another series for you lucky people...why am i uploading so many at a time, well i&#039;m only downloading a couple of films, so i want to make sure i&#039;m sending enough to cover what i&#039;m taking.

Once again, i&#039;ve ripped using dvdshrink, with nothing removed, sorry it&#039;s only in english, with no subs, but hey, what the heck, it&#039;s a great series anyway.

Well, if these go as well as the other series i&#039;ve done, i&#039;ll put up the last series in a couple of days...if they don&#039;t, well, i&#039;ll still put them up.

As many others are doing Only Fools & Horses, i shalln&#039;t bother with the rest (unless specifically asked for), instead i&#039;ll finish off May to December, then follow it with  You Rang M&#039;lord.

All comments are welcome, if i&#039;ve missed something, i&#039;m sorry, if you want something, let me know and if i have it i&#039;ll share it.

Have fun...enjoy,
and please seed as soon as you can for as long as you can.
